      <body>
         <listPerson>
            <person sex="1">
               <persName xml:id="n1" xml:lang="ar">محمد بن يوسف بن مسدي المهلبي</persName>
               <persName corresp="#n1" type="transliterated">Muḥammad b. Yūsuf b. Masdī al-Muhallabī</persName>
               <persName>
                  <roleName type="title">Imām </roleName>
               </persName>
               <floruit>7th / 13th century <note>Formed with Sufi masters, he entered the Zaydi sect  (ši'í) and they named him Imām and ḫaṭīb. He was the author of a biographical dictionary of his masters that has not beeen preserved. He was killed at his home in Mecca.</note>
               </floruit>
               <birth evidence="internal" calendar="hijri" when-custom="0599-12-10">0599-12-10 </birth>
               <death evidence="internal" calendar="hijri" when-custom="0673-10-11">0673-10-11 </death>
               <note>
                  
                     Place of birth
                  : <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC0103IHA">al-Andalus</placeName>
                  
                  
                     Place of death
                  : <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC0026IHA">Mecca / Makka al-Mukarrama</placeName>
                  
                  
                     
                  : <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC0020IHA">Damascus / Dimašq</placeName>
                  
                     
                  : <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC0013IHA">Alexandria / al-Iskandariyya</placeName>
                  
                     
                  : <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC0029IHA">Medina / al-Madīna al-Munawwara</placeName>
               </note>
            </person>
